values: i had a pretty cool end of november :D yay! lol. and im in a really good mood. i have been all day. lol. go me! teeehee. so anyways. i dont know what...someone must have put something in my cereal this morning or something :D and TAG today was cool. we had a sub for a tag teacher. then we had the intruder and fire drill durning :) i liked the walking back the best :D lol. i LOVE the left arm!! teehee. god i dont know whats gotten into me. oh well. and i dont have to do anything tonite...other then the lab and 1000 chemistry problems. FUN! i know. but it shouldnt be too bad. god...is that optimisim i detect??? :D thats what you get for being in a good mood. :D so im like extremely happy right now. no one take that away. because i wanna stay in my good moood. and i wanna just sit here and chill all day and not have to deal with anything cuz its the best thing ever. thats wat tag's for. oh i love tag. i hate that its ending next week. oh well...theres always next semester. and yes christian, you can choose the seminar :D lucky you ;)

ok. well um...? iunno. u can prolly tell im having a harder time expressing myself on here. but well...iunno. life...has been ok. good and bad. take the good, learn from the bad. :D lol. wat am i? a fortune cookie? lol. but its true. ive been incredibly happy, sad, and TOTALLY out of it. sry christian :D lol. and i keep disapearing on people. anna's brothers hissing at her, i mean her dog. lol so i guess im in a good mood right now, but its liable to change. im well...i feel bad about some things that i cant say on here. but i really respect my friends. and i...well im really grateful for all of them. i really love you guys and you have no idea. whether you care, or not. or even ready to embrace that fact. i honestly love you guys. and i hope you all know that. because you guys know who i am and i want everyone else to know that too. u guys have helped me find who i am, and more importantly let me show myself to people. and i love talking to you, and growing up with you. i was listening to a song and i kept thinking about well..things. life in highschool with you guys. it wouldnt be anywhere near as good without you. so while im being such a looser, let me say one more thing. i dont expect anything in return, besides, im not very good at recieving love back. i just know how to give it. but i do love you all. and i hope you know that. 

ok im done. i think. :D see you at school tomorow

im lonely. i hate being alone.

i didnt know you could miss people sooooooo much until it was a physical pain....no..no one's died. thank god. i just...missed certain people BEYOND belief this week. gave me time to think....so . i went to my granparents house though. and it snowed! i took pics so YAY! i love snow. well...until u get tired of it. there was snow on the ground all four days...got repetitive. :D my uncle and his wife came in and my step cousin. my step cousin is 7 and he's so funny but its sad. cuz his mums really mean to him. not like abusive. she just doesnt let him be a kid. me and my sisters changed that ;) lol. im just glad to be home. never thought i'd be happy to. or be happy to see this monday coming. gosh. missing someone is like...a sickness. takes over your brain. i wish hugs could be given over a computer..or fone. cuz were i am, theyre in short supply

hmm well today was not...good. but it wasnt bad either. iunno. it was half and half. i actually felt like myself today. so maybe i've gotten over the major part of the hill. so i'll just enjoy my trip down before another hill appears. so yeah it was cool getting back to my old self, talking to christian and biz, then later on anna. umm girl scouts was gay today and i wasnt happy. at all. *dies* well anyways. now im sitting here alone and for somereason i feel sooooo...selfish. i do. i know what im feeling selfish about. but i dont know /why/. gah. stupidness. but yes. *shrugs* and its not like i can /talk/ to anyone at the moment since everyones gone. there we go again with the selfishness...

ok. well it's been two months today since my bday. and gahhhhhhh i wish i could go back to fourteen....ARGh. well anyways. intersting two days. DIED in school. like i cryed durning lunch and i was just sick of everything. but i got a hug i guess u could call it and it made me feel better. then i went to the play with christian and ashka and we saw bridget there...along with ms marcy, ms holt, and ms carpenter...who sat beside us. lol. :D and then today was pretty cool dood. i was hyper. other people were not. LETS PLAY STAY AWAY!! trolly rides ;) and Piss for Passport....lol. there was a book that said P is for Passport...ok. i know. :D the HP movie was FUNNY. we were cracking up. overall it was cool although i want to give two..no wait three people really really big hugs. i bet u can guess who

have you ever felt like u gave so much but never recieved anything back? i dont think im /capable/ of recieving.....i dont know. but for some reason i feel so...empty. a part of me is missing. and i keep trying to find out who i am....but i cant...i just cant. and i hate that. i wish i knew who i was. i used to..but ive seemed to have lost that person. *sighs* i dont know. at least i have friends to fall back on. too bad they cant help me look for me

well, today is monday. i was soooooooo like grrrrr at the world today. yeah. all the way to the fifth r. lol. but really. i was just in a bad mood. and i dont know why either...well. i /had/ just figured out i had a C in spanish right before it. but i dont think that was the full reason. and then today i realized how....selfish i was. i sit here complaining every day about my inner conflicts while there are people who are having real ones. real LIFE ones. that actually happen, just not some conflict witin yourself. and when i realize that i think i feel guilty. i dont think i should be complaining all the time while there are people i know with much more real life termoil going on....i dont know. sometimes i think of myself too much. *sigh* o.o

sometimes i wish the whole world would go away and i'd just be ALONE. alone to think. alone to cry. alone to wonder what the hell is going on!!! alone. but id never be able to do that. i need people to much. two people in paticular. but sometimes i wanna shut myself off. i want my own private mountain. i want to just crawl in a corner and sleep. i just dont want to deal with it anymore. everything either ticks me off, makes me sad, or puts me into the happiest happy ive ever been in. its a deep contrast. i wish i could find my middle ground. maybe if i was alone with me myself and i, i could find myself. i could find my middle ground. i cant find my "happy place". does anyone know where i can find one. am i alone in it? i dont know. i guess i dont wish i were alone. i wish you were here. but ur working :( *sigh*

i looked up the word friendship in the dictionary and it said: n. the state of being friends. So i looked up the word friends and it said A person whom one knows, likes, and trusts or one who supports, and sympathizes.  But i dont know. do you agree? and if so look around you. who could you call a friend?? to me its someone who wont only make sure u dont fall, but will be there to catch you if you do. i look around and sometimes im not sure of who will catch me. i know a few. they know who they are. but...what about the rest. and what about me? who am i a friend to? who do i help? i dont know. sometimes i wish i was all knowing. maybe then things wouldnt be confusing. then i would know who my friends are. but as of now. its trial and error.

dont you wish that you could go back. maybe to two seconds ago. maybe back 3 years. 

dont you wish life was still uncomplicated and innocent. where the only hard thing was figuring out if you had cooties or not.

dont you wish that life would be fair for once and made everyone happy

dont you wish you werent confused anymore and all the pieces seemed to fit into the big picture

dont you wish that at times you were somewhere else. that place you seek in your dreams?

dont you wish that maybe just maybe there is a reason we were here and there was a way to understand everything you wanted too

dont you wish i would shutup? ;) im just blabbing anyways.

does anyone look at something and go "that is life"? no, not one person. *sigh* and that makes me sad. i believe that people are now blind...blind to life. generations of evolution has taken away our site. I wish i could show people how /i/ see things. but it would be pointless. a blind man will never see again...at least not in the same way. But its sad. because if people could see life would there be all the problems of today? crime? war? hatred? life wasnt created so we could destroy it. life is ironic. i dont think the world understand the irony. just like living is one big joke that no one finds funny anymore. im just trying to live, laugh, and enjoy. life is for living.
